===Pronunciation===
* Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɒʃə(r)|-ɒʃə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Something that [[wash]]es; especially an [[appliance]] such as a [[washing machine]] or [[dishwasher]].
# A person who washes for a [[living]]; a [[washerwoman]].
# A [[flat]] [[disk]], placed beneath a [[nut]] or at some [[joint]], to [[distribute]] [[pressure]], [[relieve]] [[friction]] or [[prevent]] [[leakage]].
# A [[face cloth]].

